<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich VII. von Gera</head><p>Der Rat teilt wegen der Herren von Waldenfels Unkenntnis mit und bietet Vermittlung an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_500" id="249v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_500_r1l24"><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> cʒü Gera / </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_500_r1l25"><expan>Edl<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> / Als Jr vns <expan>verſchr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> <expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> VValdenfelſer </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l26"> <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan> / . von <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſache 
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan></del> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir vor nicht </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l28">gewiſʒet / So ſind ſie 
<del rend="strikethrough">vn nicht </del>
<add><ab facs="#facs_500_line_1576352195695_5190"><expan>wed<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab></add> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l29">auch ſüſt mit Jn nicht cʒeſchıcken / Alſo / daʒ vvir Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l30">nicht mechtig ſein / <expan>Möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vvir <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan> darcʒü ıht getün </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l31">daʒ ſich cʒü güt vnd frewntſchaft cʒüg Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l32">vnd wo wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan> <expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lıeb vnd dinſt <expan>beweıſ<ex>en</ex></expan> <expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_500_r1l35">Das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir 
<add><ab facs="#facs_500_line_1576352222681_5207">auch </ab></add> <expan>ſünderlıch<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan> / <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ı<ex>n</ex></expan> dıe Sıxtȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_500" id="249v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> czü Gera
                    </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>Edl<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re,</expan> als ir uns
                            <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> habt <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>d<ex>er</ex></expan> Waldenfelser <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, von
                                <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sache
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir vor nicht gewiszet, so sind sie
                                    <add><expan>wed<ex>er</ex></expan></add>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> auch süst
                        mit in nicht cze schicken, also daz wir ir nicht mechtig sein.
                                <expan>Möcht<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
                        darczü iht getün, daz sich czü güt und frewntschaft czüg, das
                                <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir <expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. Und
                        wo wir <expan>ew<ex>r</ex>n</expan>
<expan>gnad<ex>e</ex>n</expan> lieb und dinst
                            <expan>beweis<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>möht<ex>en</ex></expan>, das <expan>tet<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                            <add>auch</add>
<expan>sünderlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>ne</expan>. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>i<ex>n</ex></expan> die Sixti.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
